place.name: LANTEGLOS BY CAMELFORD
place.gazetteerText: Lanteglos by Camelford, par., Cornwall, 3951 ac., pop. 1524; contains the town of Camelford. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
